            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Immediate response</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Consultation booking</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Pre-qualification</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-cyan-50 to-teal-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-cyan-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M9 12h6m-6 4h6m2 5H7a2 2 0 01-2-2V5a2 2 0 012-2h5.586a1 1 0 01.707.293l5.414 5.414a1 1 0 01.293.707V19a2 2 0 01-2 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Document Collection</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Automated reminders get documents in without manual chase.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Document checklists</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Reminder sequences</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Secure upload links</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-teal-50 to-green-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-teal-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M8 7V3m8 4V3m-9 8h10M5 21h14a2 2 0 002-2V7a2 2 0 00-2-2H5a2 2 0 00-2 2v12a2 2 0 002 2z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Year-Round Engagement</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Stay top-of-mind with tax tips, deadline reminders, and planning prompts.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Tax tip emails</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Deadline reminders</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Planning invitations</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
        
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-green-50 to-blue-50 p-8 rounded-2xl">
          <div class="w-14 h-14 bg-green-600 rounded-xl flex items-center justify-center mb-6">
            <svg class="w-7 h-7 text-white" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24">
              <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M12 4.354a4 4 0 110 5.292M15 21H3v-1a6 6 0 0112 0v1zm0 0h6v-1a6 6 0 00-9-5.197m13.5-9a2.25 2.25 0 11-4.5 0 2.25 2.25 0 014.5 0z"></path>
            </svg>
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-slate-900 mb-3">Referral Generation</h3>
          <p class="text-slate-600 mb-4">Systematic referral asks after every successful engagement.</p>
          <ul class="space-y-2 text-slate-700">
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Post-filing requests</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Referral incentives</li>
            <li class="flex items-center"><svg class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mr-2" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" viewBox="0 0 24 24"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M5 13l4 4L19 7"></path></svg>Review collection</li>
          </ul>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- Testimonial -->
  <section class="py-16 md:py-24 bg-slate-50">
    <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6">
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto">
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-blue-50 to-cyan-50 p-8 md:p-12 rounded-2xl">
